<div class="help">
<p>This page shows the segments & donor statuses currently being generated by WMF code</p>
<p>This is work towards <a target="_blank" href="https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/T336305">donor segments</a>
and the segments described in this <a target="_blank" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qM36MeKWyOENl-iR5umuLph5HLHG6W_6c46xJUdE3QY/edit#gid=1786541006"> google doc</a>
</p>
<p>The current implementation is simpler than the google doc - such that it
defines 2 measures - segment and status and the statuses do not depend on the segment.
As with the google specification only the first code will be applied</p>
<p>Note that the 2 dimensions are numbered such that they could
be combined for a unique segment - eg. 150 would be a lapsed major donor</p>
</div>

  <h3>Segments</h3>
<table class="row-highlight">
  {foreach from=$segments item='segment'}
      <tr>
        <td>{$segment.label}</td>
        <td>{$segment.description|nl2br}</td>
      </tr>
  {/foreach}
</table>

<h3>Statuses</h3>
<table class="row-highlight">
    {foreach from=$statuses item='status'}
      <tr>
        <td>{$status.label}</td>
        <td>{$status.description|nl2br}</td>
      </tr>
    {/foreach}
</table>
